short.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G: ProxyStar allows you set ip proxy information.http, https, socks4 and socks5 proxies are supported.

long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
A simple extension to quickly switch your proxy servers.
Support to update proxy information via URL link.
Support to import proxy information from the clipboard.
Import example:
ip:port
protocol://ip:port
protocol,ip,port
...
